title: Talks Machina: Discussing C1E98 - The Mines of the Many
description: On this episode of Talks Machina, Brian Wayne Foster is joined by Laura Bailey, Marisha Ray, and Liam O'Brien discuss CR #98 and answer questions about Galdric, Kiki's leadership, and more!
